repeat:
repeat(func: Function, n: number) → {Function}

Returns a new function which when applied to an argument, has the same effect as applying the specified function to the same argument n times.
thrice:
thrice(func: Function) → {Function}

Returns a new function which when applied to an argument, has the same effect as applying the specified function to the same argument 3 times.
twice:
twice(func: Function) → {Function}

Returns a new function which when applied to an argument, has the same effect as applying the specified function to the same argument 2 times.
